Patch Notes Version 1.0

* Fixed bug that caused player to respawn on death (Lava Grinder)
* Fixed animations playing weirdly when doing certain actions
* Fixed a bug from the Ragdoll Handler that would break your character when you respawned or joined
* Reduced lag spikes during pushing a player or getting close to a ragdolled player
* Fixed the map's not showing on the Voting UI
* Disabled Shiftlock for game breaking issues
* Fixed lag from pressing Q to grab a ragdolled player
* Fixed certain Security issues from exploiters
* Fixed a bug where you fell off a map you would not respawn
* Dropkicking now only goes to one direction
* Disabled gears from lagging the game & abusing it
* Fixed bug where ragdoll would work on a certain avatar
